<main>No API other than <a href="https://developer.twitter.com/en/docs/twitter-api/users/lookup/api-reference/get-users-me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GET /2/users/me</a> will be used.<br>Therefore, information other than <a href="https://developer.twitter.com/en/docs/twitter-api/users/lookup/api-reference/get-users-me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GET /2/users/me</a>, i.e., id, name, username, will not be retrieved.<br>Twitter Authentication is required <b>once a week</b>.</main>